org.apache.poi.hssf.record

Class BoundSheetRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.RecordBase
      • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.Record
        • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.StandardRecord
          • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.BoundSheetRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public final class BoundSheetRecord
extends StandardRecord
    Defines a sheet within a workbook. Basically stores the sheet name and tells where the Beginning of file record is within the HSSF file.(定义工作簿中的工作表。基本上存储工作表名称并告诉HSSF文件中文件开始记录的位置。)

      • serialize

        public void serialize(LittleEndianOutput out)
        Description copied from class: StandardRecord
        Write the data content of this BIFF record. The 'ushort sid' and 'ushort size' header fields have already been written by the superclass.

        The number of bytes written must equal the record size reported by RecordBase.getRecordSize()} minus four ( record header consisting of a 'ushort sid' and 'ushort reclength' has already been written by their superclass).

        (写入此BIFF记录的数据内容。超类已经编写了“ushort sid”和“ushort size”标头字段。写入的字节数必须等于RecordBase报告的记录大小。getRecordSize（）}减四（由“ushort sid”和“ushort reclong”组成的记录头已由其超类写入）。)
        Specified by:
        serialize in class StandardRecord(在StandardRecord类中序列化)
